{"id":"cli/config","title":"ng config","contents":"\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/config\", \"name\": \"config\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-config\">ng config<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/config#ng-config\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>Retrieves or sets Angular configuration values in the angular.json file for the workspace.</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">config</span> [<var>json-path</var>] [<var>value</var>]\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------description----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        Description\n    </h2>\n    <p>A workspace has a single CLI configuration file, <code>angular.json</code>, at the top level.\nThe <code>projects</code> object contains a configuration object for each project in the workspace.</p>\n<p>You can edit the configuration directly in a code editor,\nor indirectly on the command line using this command.</p>\n<p>The configurable property names match command option names,\nexcept that in the configuration file, all names must use camelCase,\nwhile on the command line options can be given dash-case.</p>\n<p>For further details, see <a href=\"guide/workspace-config\">Workspace Configuration</a>.</p>\n<p>For configuration of CLI usage analytics, see <a href=\"cli/analytics\">ng analytics</a>.</p>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">参数</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"width:15%\">参数</th>\n      <th style=\"width:40%\">说明</th>\n      <th>值类型</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">json-path</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>要设置或查询的配置键，采用 JSON 路径格式。例如：<code>a[3].foo.bar[2]</code>。如果没有提供新值，则返回此键的当前值。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">value</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>如果提供，则为指定配置键的新值。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">选项</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th style=\"width:15%\">选项</th>\n    <th style=\"width:40%\">说明</th>\n    <th>值类型</th>\n    <th>默认值</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--global</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>访问此调用者 home 目录下的全局配置。</p>\n\n      <p><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名:</span> -g</p>\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在控制台显示关于本命令的帮助信息。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/workspace-config\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/analytics\n - cli/config#ng-config\n - guide/workspace-config\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md\n-->"}